title: Eero Gen 2 Discussion with CEO and Co-Founder Nick Weaver
description:
In this video we interview Nick Weaver, co-founder and CEO of Eero; one of the most innovative mesh network systems available today.  With new generation 2 products like the Beacon, expanding your home network is made simple with Eero.

See Abt's selection of Eero products here: http://www.abt.com/brand-category/eero/Wireless-Routers/1143/2393.html?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=video&utm_campaign=EERO%20_20170721
